  'Launch: Intensive Day 2 - Vision + Audio',
  'Day 2 guidance email. Focus: build vision, create activation audio.',
  'intensive',
  'active',
  'Today: Build your Vision + Activation Audio',
  E'<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang="en">\n<head>\n  <meta charset="UTF-8">\n  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">\n</head>\n<body style="margin:0;padding:0;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,''Segoe UI'',Roboto,''Helvetica Neue'',Arial,sans-serif;background-color:#000;color:#fff;">\n<table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background-color:#000;">\n<tr><td align="center" style="padding:40px 20px;">\n<table width="600" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="max-width:600px;">\n\n<tr><td style="padding:0 0 24px;text-align:center;">\n  <div style="display:inline-block;padding:8px 24px;background-color:rgba(57,255,20,0.1);border-radius:50px;border:2px solid #39FF14;">\n    <p style="margin:0;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#39FF14;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1px;">Day 2 of 3</p>\n  </div>\n</td></tr>\n\n<tr><td style="padding:0;">\n<div style="padding:40px;background-color:#1F1F1F;border-radius:16px;border:2px solid #39FF14;">\n\n  <h1 style="margin:0 0 24px;font-size:28px;font-weight:bold;color:#fff;line-height:1.2;">Vision + Audio</h1>\n\n  <p style="margin:0 0 16px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#E5E5E5;">Hi {{firstName}},</p>\n  <p style="margin:0 0 24px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#E5E5E5;">Nice work getting your foundations in place.</p>\n\n  <div style="margin:0 0 24px;padding:24px;background-color:#000;border-radius:12px;border:2px solid #39FF14;">\n    <p style="margin:0 0 16px;font-size:11px;color:#39FF14;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1px;font-weight:600;">Today''s Focus</p>\n    <p style="margin:0 0 16px;font-size:16px;color:#fff;font-weight:600;">Turn your answers into a clear Life Vision and your first Activation Audio.</p>\n    <p style="margin:0 0 6px;font-size:14px;color:#E5E5E5;">&#8226; Build Your Life Vision (12 Categories)</p>\n    <p style="margin:0 0 6px;font-size:14px;color:#E5E5E5;">&#8226; Refine Your Vision with VIVA</p>\n    <p style="margin:0 0 6px;font-size:14px;color:#E5E5E5;">&#8226; Generate Your Activation Audio</p>\n    <p style="margin:0 0 6px;font-size:14px;color:#E5E5E5;">&#8226; Record Your Voice</p>\n    <p style="margin:0;font-size:14px;color:#E5E5E5;">&#8226; Create an Audio Mix</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin-bottom:24px;"><tr><td align="center">\n    <a href="https://vibrationfit.com/auth/login" style="display:inline-block;padding:18px 48px;background-color:#39FF14;color:#000;text-decoration:none;font-size:16px;font-weight:700;border-radius:50px;">Go to My Intensive &rarr;</a>\n  </td></tr></table>\n\n  <p style="margin:0 0 24px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6;color:#E5E5E5;">By the end of today, you''ll have a <strong style="color:#39FF14;">personalized audio</strong> you can listen to on repeat to stay in harmony with your vision.</p>\n\n  <div style="padding:16px;background-color:rgba(20,184,166,0.1);border-radius:12px;border:2px solid #14B8A6;">\n    <p style="margin:0 0 8px;font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:#14B8A6;">Hit something confusing or broken?</p>\n    <p style="margin:0 0 3px;font-size:13px;color:#E5E5E5;">&#8226; Click the Support button or go to <a href="https://vibrationfit.com/support" style="color:#39FF14;text-decoration:none;">vibrationfit.com/support</a></p>\n    <p style="margin:0 0 3px;font-size:13px;color:#E5E5E5;">&#8226; Choose "Bug Report" if something isn''t working</p>\n    <p style="margin:0;font-size:13px;color:#E5E5E5;">&#8226; Your feedback is shaping how thousands will experience this later</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <div style="height:2px;background-color:#39FF14;margin:32px 0;"></div>\n  <p style="margin:0;font-size:15px;color:#E5E5E5;">You''re doing the real work,<br>The Vibration Fit Team</p>\n\n</div>\n</td></tr>\n\n<tr><td style="padding:32px 20px 0;text-align:center;">\n  <p style="margin:0 0 8px;font-size:11px;color:#666;">Vibration Fit &middot; <span style="color:#39FF14;">Above the Green Line</span></p>\n  <p style="margin:0;font-size:10px;color:#555;">You''re receiving this because you purchased the 72-Hour Activation Intensive.</p>\n</td></tr>\n\n</table>\n</td></tr>\n</table>\n</body>\n</html>',
  E'DAY 2: BUILD YOUR VISION + ACTIVATION AUDIO\n\nHi {{firstName}},\n\nNice work getting your foundations in place.\n\nTODAY''S FOCUS\nTurn your answers into a clear Life Vision and your first Activation Audio.\n\n- Build Your Life Vision (12 Categories)\n- Refine Your Vision with VIVA\n- Generate Your Activation Audio\n- Record Your Voice\n- Create an Audio Mix\n\nGo to My Intensive: https://vibrationfit.com/auth/login\n\nBy the end of today, you''ll have a personalized audio you can listen to on repeat.\n\nHit something confusing or broken?\n- Go to vibrationfit.com/support\n- Choose "Bug Report" if something isn''t working\n\nYou''re doing the real work,\nThe Vibration Fit Team',
  '["firstName"]'::jsonb,
  '["Scheduled: Day 2 after intensive start (T+24h)"]'::jsonb
),

