(
  'launch-intensive-day3',
  'Launch: Intensive Day 3 - Activation + Completion',
  'Day 3 guidance email. Focus: vision board, journal, calibration call, unlock platform.',
  'intensive',
  'active',
  'Today: Activate your vision & unlock your platform',
  E'<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang="en">\n<head>\n  <meta charset="UTF-8">\n  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">\n</head>\n<body style="margin:0;padding:0;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,''Segoe UI'',Roboto,''Helvetica Neue'',Arial,sans-serif;background-color:#000;color:#fff;">\n<table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background-color:#000;">\n<tr><td align="center" style="padding:40px 20px;">\n<table width="600" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="max-width:600px;">\n\n<tr><td style="padding:0 0 24px;text-align:center;">\n  <div style="display:inline-block;padding:8px 24px;background-color:rgba(57,255,20,0.1);border-radius:50px;border:2px solid #39FF14;">\n    <p style="margin:0;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#39FF14;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1px;">Day 3 of 3 &mdash; Final Stretch</p>\n  </div>\n</td></tr>\n\n<tr><td style="padding:0;">\n<div style="padding:40px;background-color:#1F1F1F;border-radius:16px;border:2px solid #39FF14;">\n\n  <h1 style="margin:0 0 24px;font-size:28px;font-weight:bold;color:#fff;line-height:1.2;">Activation + Completion</h1>\n\n  <p style="margin:0 0 16px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#E5E5E5;">Hi {{firstName}},</p>\n  <p style="margin:0 0 16px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#E5E5E5;">You''re in the final stretch of your <strong style="color:#39FF14;">72-Hour Activation Intensive</strong>.</p>\n  <p style="margin:0 0 24px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#E5E5E5;">By the end of today, you''ll have your vision <strong>activated</strong> and your full Vibration Fit platform <strong>unlocked.</strong></p>\n\n  <div style="margin:0 0 24px;padding:24px;background-color:#000;border-radius:12px;border:2px solid #39FF14;">\n    <p style="margin:0 0 16px;font-size:11px;color:#39FF14;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1px;font-weight:600;">Today''s Focus</p>\n    <p style="margin:0 0 12px;font-size:15px;color:#E5E5E5;"><strong style="color:#fff;">Activation (Steps 10-12)</strong></p>\n    <p style="margin:0 0 3px;font-size:14px;color:#E5E5E5;padding-left:16px;">&#8226; Vision Board</p>\n    <p style="margin:0 0 3px;font-size:14px;color:#E5E5E5;padding-left:16px;">&#8226; Journal Entry</p>\n    <p style="margin:0 0 16px;font-size:14px;color:#E5E5E5;padding-left:16px;">&#8226; Book Calibration Call</p>\n    <p style="margin:0 0 12px;font-size:15px;color:#E5E5E5;"><strong style="color:#fff;">Completion (Steps 13-14)</strong></p>\n    <p style="margin:0 0 3px;font-size:14px;color:#E5E5E5;padding-left:16px;">&#8226; MAP (My Activation Plan)</p>\n    <p style="margin:0;font-size:14px;color:#39FF14;font-weight:600;padding-left:16px;">&#8226; Unlock Platform</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin-bottom:24px;"><tr><td align="center">\n    <a href="https://vibrationfit.com/auth/login" style="display:inline-block;padding:18px 48px;background-color:#39FF14;color:#000;text-decoration:none;font-size:16px;font-weight:700;border-radius:50px;">Go to My Next Step &rarr;</a>\n  </td></tr></table>\n\n  <div style="margin:0 0 24px;padding:24px;background-color:#000;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid #333;">\n    <p style="margin:0 0 12px;font-size:16px;font-weight:600;color:#fff;">What "Unlock Platform" actually does</p>\n    <p style="margin:0 0 8px;font-size:14px;color:#E5E5E5;">When you reach Step 14, you''ll see:</p>\n    <p style="margin:0 0 4px;font-size:14px;color:#E5E5E5;">&#8226; A Journey Summary with green checks across all 14 steps</p>\n    <p style="margin:0 0 4px;font-size:14px;color:#E5E5E5;">&#8226; An Activation Snapshot comparing now vs. when you started</p>\n    <p style="margin:0 0 4px;font-size:14px;color:#E5E5E5;">&#8226; One question: "What feels most different for you?" (video or text)</p>\n    <p style="margin:0 0 12px;font-size:14px;color:#E5E5E5;">&#8226; A simple choice on how we can share your success</p>\n    <p style="margin:0 0 8px;font-size:14px;color:#E5E5E5;">When you click <strong style="color:#39FF14;">Unlock Platform</strong>:</p>\n    <p style="margin:0 0 4px;font-size:14px;color:#E5E5E5;">&#10003; Your Intensive is marked completed</p>\n    <p style="margin:0 0 4px;font-size:14px;color:#E5E5E5;">&#10003; Your main dashboard unlocks</p>\n    <p style="margin:0;font-size:14px;color:#E5E5E5;">&#10003; You get the full Vibration Fit experience</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <p style="margin:0 0 24px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6;color:#E5E5E5;">This is your graduation moment. Give yourself one focused block today. Don''t leave your story half-written.</p>\n\n  <div style="padding:16px;background-color:rgba(20,184,166,0.1);border-radius:12px;border:2px solid #14B8A6;">\n    <p style="margin:0;font-size:13px;color:#E5E5E5;">If anything is confusing or broken, go to <a href="https://vibrationfit.com/support" style="color:#39FF14;text-decoration:none;">vibrationfit.com/support</a> and choose "Bug Report" so we can fix it fast.</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <div style="height:2px;background-color:#39FF14;margin:32px 0;"></div>\n  <p style="margin:0;font-size:15px;color:#E5E5E5;">You''ve come all this way. Finish the path and step into the platform you just built for your future self.</p>\n  <p style="margin:16px 0 0;font-size:15px;color:#E5E5E5;">With you,<br>The Vibration Fit Team</p>\n\n</div>\n</td></tr>\n\n<tr><td style="padding:32px 20px 0;text-align:center;">\n  <p style="margin:0 0 8px;font-size:11px;color:#666;">Vibration Fit &middot; <span style="color:#39FF14;">Above the Green Line</span></p>\n  <p style="margin:0;font-size:10px;color:#555;">You''re receiving this because you purchased the 72-Hour Activation Intensive.</p>\n</td></tr>\n\n</table>\n</td></tr>\n</table>\n</body>\n</html>',
  E'DAY 3: ACTIVATE YOUR VISION & UNLOCK YOUR PLATFORM\n\nHi {{firstName}},\n\nYou''re in the final stretch of your 72-Hour Activation Intensive.\n\nBy the end of today, you''ll have your vision activated and your full Vibration Fit platform unlocked.\n\nTODAY''S FOCUS\n\nActivation (Steps 10-12)\n- Vision Board\n- Journal Entry\n- Book Calibration Call\n\nCompletion (Steps 13-14)\n- MAP (My Activation Plan)\n- Unlock Platform\n\nGo to My Next Step: https://vibrationfit.com/auth/login\n\nWHAT "UNLOCK PLATFORM" DOES\nWhen you reach Step 14, you''ll see:\n- A Journey Summary with green checks across all 14 steps\n- An Activation Snapshot comparing now vs. when you started\n- One question: "What feels most different for you?"\n- A simple choice on how we can share your success\n\nWhen you click Unlock Platform:\n- Your Intensive is marked completed\n- Your main dashboard unlocks\n- You get the full Vibration Fit experience\n\nThis is your graduation moment. Don''t leave your story half-written.\n\nWith you,\nThe Vibration Fit Team',
  '["firstName"]'::jsonb,
  '["Scheduled: Day 3 after intensive start (T+48h)"]'::jsonb
),

-- -------------------------------------------------------
-- 8. Day 4 - Debrief + Testimonial (conditional)
-- -------------------------------------------------------
(
  'launch-intensive-day4-debrief',
  'Launch: Intensive Day 4 - Debrief / Unlock Rescue',
  'Conditional email for almost-finishers who haven''t completed Unlock Platform. Only send if started but unlock_completed != true.',
  'intensive',
  'active',
  'Final step: unlock your platform & capture your results',
  E'<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang="en">\n<head>\n  <meta charset="UTF-8">\n  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">\n</head>\n<body style="margin:0;padding:0;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,''Segoe UI'',Roboto,''Helvetica Neue'',Arial,sans-serif;background-color:#000;color:#fff;">\n<table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background-color:#000;">\n<tr><td align="center" style="padding:40px 20px;">\n<table width="600" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="max-width:600px;">\n\n<tr><td style="padding:0 0 24px;text-align:center;">\n  <div style="display:inline-block;padding:8px 24px;background-color:rgba(57,255,20,0.1);border-radius:50px;border:2px solid #39FF14;">\n    <p style="margin:0;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#39FF14;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1px;">Step 14 of 14</p>\n  </div>\n</td></tr>\n\n<tr><td style="padding:0;">\n<div style="padding:40px;background-color:#1F1F1F;border-radius:16px;border:2px solid #39FF14;">\n\n  <h1 style="margin:0 0 24px;font-size:28px;font-weight:bold;color:#fff;line-height:1.2;">One last step: Unlock Platform</h1>\n\n  <p style="margin:0 0 16px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#E5E5E5;">Hi {{firstName}},</p>\n  <p style="margin:0 0 16px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#E5E5E5;">I can see you''ve made it all the way through your <strong style="color:#39FF14;">72-Hour Activation Intensive</strong>.</p>\n  <p style="margin:0 0 24px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#E5E5E5;">There''s one last step: <strong style="color:#39FF14;">Unlock Platform</strong>. This is Step 14 of 14, and it does two things at once:</p>\n\n  <div style="margin:0 0 16px;padding:24px;background-color:#000;border-radius:12px;border:2px solid #39FF14;">\n    <p style="margin:0 0 12px;font-size:16px;font-weight:600;color:#39FF14;">1. Captures your before/after</p>\n    <p style="margin:0 0 4px;font-size:14px;color:#E5E5E5;">You''ll answer a short set of questions so the system can compare your post-intensive answers with your original Baseline Intake:</p>\n    <p style="margin:8px 0 3px;font-size:14px;color:#E5E5E5;">&#8226; How clear your vision feels now</p>\n    <p style="margin:0 0 3px;font-size:14px;color:#E5E5E5;">&#8226; How empowered you are to stay in vibrational harmony</p>\n    <p style="margin:0 0 3px;font-size:14px;color:#E5E5E5;">&#8226; How easy it is to create and update your vision, audios, and board</p>\n    <p style="margin:0;font-size:14px;color:#E5E5E5;">&#8226; How clear your MAP feels</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <div style="margin:0 0 24px;padding:24px;background-color:#000;border-radius:12px;border:2px solid #39FF14;">\n    <p style="margin:0 0 12px;font-size:16px;font-weight:600;color:#39FF14;">2. Graduates you &amp; unlocks your full platform</p>\n    <p style="margin:0 0 3px;font-size:14px;color:#E5E5E5;">&#10003; Your Intensive is marked <strong style="color:#fff;">completed</strong></p>\n    <p style="margin:0 0 3px;font-size:14px;color:#E5E5E5;">&#10003; Your main dashboard <strong style="color:#fff;">unlocks</strong></p>\n    <p style="margin:0;font-size:14px;color:#E5E5E5;">&#10003; You''ll see a celebration state and your full VibrationFit experience opens up</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin-bottom:24px;"><tr><td align="center">\n    <a href="https://vibrationfit.com/auth/login" style="display:inline-block;padding:18px 48px;background-color:#39FF14;color:#000;text-decoration:none;font-size:16px;font-weight:700;border-radius:50px;">Complete Unlock Platform &rarr;</a>\n  </td></tr></table>\n\n  <p style="margin:0 0 8px;font-size:16px;font-weight:600;color:#fff;">What we''ll ask you</p>\n  <p style="margin:0 0 4px;font-size:14px;color:#E5E5E5;">&#8226; A Journey Summary showing green checks across all 14 steps</p>\n  <p style="margin:0 0 4px;font-size:14px;color:#E5E5E5;">&#8226; An Activation Snapshot with 11 quick questions</p>\n  <p style="margin:0 0 4px;font-size:14px;color:#E5E5E5;">&#8226; One final question: "What feels most different for you?" (video or text)</p>\n  <p style="margin:0 0 24px;font-size:14px;color:#E5E5E5;">&#8226; How (or if) we can share your success: with first name, anonymously, or not at all</p>\n\n  <div style="padding:20px;background-color:#000;border-radius:12px;border-left:4px solid #39FF14;margin-bottom:24px;">\n    <p style="margin:0 0 8px;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:#39FF14;">Why this matters (especially as a $1 Founding Tester)</p>\n    <p style="margin:0 0 4px;font-size:14px;color:#E5E5E5;">&#8226; It gives <strong>you</strong> a clear "before vs after" snapshot to look back on later.</p>\n    <p style="margin:0;font-size:14px;color:#E5E5E5;">&#8226; It gives <strong>us</strong> the proof and insight we need to improve the platform and help more people.</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <p style="margin:0 0 24px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6;color:#E5E5E5;">You paid $1 and did the work. Finish this last step so you leave with a complete story and a fully unlocked platform.</p>\n\n  <div style="height:2px;background-color:#39FF14;margin:32px 0;"></div>\n  <p style="margin:0;font-size:15px;color:#E5E5E5;">With deep appreciation for helping us build this,<br>The Vibration Fit Team</p>\n\n  <p style="margin:24px 0 0;font-size:13px;color:#999;font-style:italic;">If anything on the Unlock page is confusing or broken, go to <a href="https://vibrationfit.com/support" style="color:#39FF14;text-decoration:none;">vibrationfit.com/support</a> and choose "Bug Report" so we can fix it fast.</p>\n\n</div>\n</td></tr>\n\n<tr><td style="padding:32px 20px 0;text-align:center;">\n  <p style="margin:0 0 8px;font-size:11px;color:#666;">Vibration Fit &middot; <span style="color:#39FF14;">Above the Green Line</span></p>\n  <p style="margin:0;font-size:10px;color:#555;">You''re receiving this because you purchased the 72-Hour Activation Intensive.</p>\n</td></tr>\n\n</table>\n</td></tr>\n</table>\n</body>\n</html>',
  E'FINAL STEP: UNLOCK YOUR PLATFORM & CAPTURE YOUR RESULTS\n\nHi {{firstName}},\n\nI can see you''ve made it all the way through your 72-Hour Activation Intensive.\n\nThere''s one last step: Unlock Platform (Step 14 of 14).\n\n1. CAPTURES YOUR BEFORE/AFTER\nYou''ll answer a short set of questions comparing now vs. your original Baseline:\n- How clear your vision feels now\n- How empowered you are to stay in vibrational harmony\n- How easy it is to create and update your vision, audios, and board\n- How clear your MAP feels\n\n2. GRADUATES YOU & UNLOCKS YOUR FULL PLATFORM\n- Your Intensive is marked completed\n- Your main dashboard unlocks\n- Your full VibrationFit experience opens up\n\nComplete Unlock Platform: https://vibrationfit.com/auth/login\n\nWHAT WE''LL ASK YOU\n- Journey Summary with green checks across all 14 steps\n- Activation Snapshot with 11 quick questions\n- "What feels most different for you?" (video or text)\n- How we can share your success (named, anonymous, or not at all)\n\nYou paid $1 and did the work. Finish this last step.\n\nWith deep appreciation,\nThe Vibration Fit Team',
  '["firstName"]'::jsonb,
  '["Conditional: only if started intensive, completed step 13, unlock_completed != true, ~60h after start"]'::jsonb
),

